description._content: SDASM.TITLE: Andrew Lech Special Collection Photo SDASM.CATALOG: Lech_00090 SDASM.DATE: 1966 SDASM.ADDITIONAL INFORMATION: Alterations since: Fokker T-2 fuselage repainted olive drab. Curtiss R3C-1 painted black with number 43. Bellanca repainted buff. Curtiss PW-8 new flight surfaces, painted silver, number A.S. 24-204. Ford Trimotor number changed from 1077 to NC-3041. Remington-Burnelli new corrugated wing surfaces. Unmarked left to right: De Haviland 4, Bristol F.2B, Salmson 2-A.2, Breguet 14 B. Santos Du-Mont Demoiselle flight surfaces painted white. Martin painted off white, umber SDASM.COLLECTION: Andrew Lech Collection SDASM.TAGS: Andrew Lech Collection PUBLIC COMMONS.SOURCE INSTITUTION: San Diego Air and Space Museum Archive
